0573237?s=20", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Prosecute Marc Elias", "last_comment_created": 1779491253430, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 9, "score_up": 301, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": false, "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 0, "created": 1779393824000, "id": "2057552946812825752", "video": false, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1989863533526618113/ZRcqJqsx_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Marc E. Elias", "username": "marceelias"}, "content": "Donald Trump recently posted that I am \"a terrible lawyer with a horrible track record.\" \ud83d\ude44\n\nIn 2020, my team and I defeated him in 64 of 65 cases.\u2696\ufe0f\n\nToday we beat DOJ in two more voter file cases. We are now 7-0.\ud83d\udcaa\n\nI guess I'm not so terrible after all...\ud83d\ude02", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 25806}, "images": [{"width": 1200, "heightRatio": 90, "url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HI61FcRakAAY4Lk.jpg", "height": 1090}], "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 35, "created": 1779448515000, "id": "2057782337480573237", "video": false, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1563734991007371266/fPdWv4Yd_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Svetlana Lokhova", "username": "RealSLokhova"}, "content": "Special Counsel Durham planned to indict Marc Elias for his participation in the anti-Trump Conspiracy. \n\nSomeone (Lisa Monaco/Maggie Goodlander) stopped the prosecutions. \n\nAG Blanche ought to:\n--immediately indict Elias, there is more than enough evidence \n--open an", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 2122}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASsZATGCo", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 27, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8634992, "raw_content": "And that goes for white people who act degenerate, too. You can't be equal to the top tier of society if you don't try to behave like the top tier of society. There are countless examples of people with all kinds of ethnicities doing it. It's not hard.", "author": "DepartmentOfOffense", "created": 1779505005943, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Deplorable_Citizen", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Equality is real simple: if you want to BE equal to white people, you must BEHAVE the way white people behave.", "last_comment_created": 1779510857986, "content": "<p>And that goes for white people who act degenerate, too. You can't be equal to the top tier of society if you don't try to behave like the top tier of society. There are countless examples of people with all kinds of ethnicities doing it. It's not hard.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 5, "score_up": 27, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASsZBZRje", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 22, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8635102, "raw_content": "Went on a job interview recently. This company produces electronic assemblies. They have about 40 people that work in the production area. The odd thing is, the city as a whole where this company is located has very few asian people. But the 40 people working in the production area are asian. Not every single one.. .but easily 95% of them are. Not just asian, but also female. There are two leads that are white men and the supervisor over this area is a white woman. I have to imagine the \"leads\" are only there to help translate documents and don't do any actual work. There's no way in hell in this city that 95% of your work force is asian. They are clearly making hiring decisions based on race. It was even mentioned during the interview that some of these people can't speak english. \n\nI believe the company might be helping to bring illegals here. I'm thinking about calling ICE. ", "author": "BillyBillington", "created": 1779508930311, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "SnowSnake", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Race based hiring", "last_comment_created": 1779524461468, "content": "<p>Went on a job interview recently. This company produces electronic assemblies. They have about 40 people that work in the production area. The odd thing is, the city as a whole where this company is located has very few asian people. But the 40 people working in the production area are asian. Not every single one.. .but easily 95% of them are. Not just asian, but also female. There are two leads that are white men and the supervisor over this area is a white woman. I have to imagine the &quot;leads&quot; are only there to help translate documents and don't do any actual work. There's no way in hell in this city that 95% of your work force is asian. They are cle